title: A set of equipment for the production of polyethylene bags (3 layers) US-SJ-60*3/FM2000

short_description: The same equipment is used in the production of polyethylene bags, popularly called cellophane bags. This US-SJ-60*3/FM2000 model equipment has a production capacity of 50-180 kg per hour, the maximum film width is 2000 mm, the film thickness is 0.03-0.10 mm, and the total weight is 8600 kg. The description below shows other models of this equipment and they differ in their patterns.
short_description_uz: Xalq tilida selofan paketlar deb nomlangan polietilen paketlar ishlab chiqarishda aynan shu uskunadan foydalaniladi. Ushbu US-SJ-60*3/FM2000 modeldagi uskuna soatiga 50-180 kg mahsulot ishlab chiqarish quvvatiga ega, plyonkaning maksimal kengligi 2000 mm, plyonka qalinligi esa 0.03-0.10 mm va umumiy vazni 8600 kg ni tashkil etadi. Quyidagi tavsifda shu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham aks etgan va ular naxlarida farqlanadi.
